data.description:
So many updates to this convenient, energy efficient, affordable home in Estacado! Super clean home with newer carpet and neutral colors makes this home move in ready! The vaulted ceilings in the living room are amazing! A few updates and improvements include the following;
 1. Roof replaced in 2017
 2. Newer HVAC 
 3. Newer fixtures in kitchen & bath 
 4. Updated lighting in living room 
 5. Newer carpet
 6. Gutters
 7. Screen protectors on Sky lights
 8. Newer energy efficient windows
 9. Newer 7 foot fence
 10. Updated kitchen cabinets, quartz, countertops & backsplash
 11. Newer appliances 
12. Newer gas line from house to alley
